d\"><a href=\"/institution/\">施設警備</a></div>\n                <div class=\"sp_nav_child\"><a href=\"/machine/\">機械警備</a></div>\n                <div class=\"sp_nav_child mgb10\"><a href=\"/traffic_guidance/\">交通誘導警備</a></div>\n            </li>\n            <li><a href=\"/info/\">お知らせ</a></li>\n        </ul>\n        <div class=\"sp_otherbtn\">\n            <a href=\"/contact/\" class=\"sp_nav_contact\"><span>お問い合わせ</span></a>\n            <a href=\"https://jsg-system.com/works/\" class=\"sp_nav_rock\"><span>社員用</span></a>\n        </div>\n    </nav>\n</div>\n    \n    <div class=\"movie\">\n        <video src=\"https://jsg-system.com/wordpress/wp-content/themes/nkh/movie.mp4\" autoplay muted loop class=\"pc_movie\"></video>\n        <video src=\"https://jsg-system.com/wordpress/wp-content/themes/nkh/movie_sp.mp4\" autoplay muted playsinline loop class=\"sp_movie\"></video>\n    </div>\n\n    <section class=\"top_infomation\">\n        <div class=\"inner\">\n            <div class=\"info_title wow animated fadeInUp\">\n                <h2 class=\"top_h2 min\"><span>NEWS</span>お知らせ</h2>\n                <div class=\"info_more info_more_pc\">\n                    <a href=\"/info/\" class=\"slidebtn\"><span class=\"slidebtn_font\">一覧を見る</span><span class=\"icon_arrow\"></span></a>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"info_wrap wow animated fadeInUp delay_fast\">\n                <ul class=\"infomation_ul\">\n\n                                                            \n                                            \n                    \n                    <li><a href=\"https://jsg-system.com/info/2026/06/14/%e5%ae%89%e5%85%a8%e9%81%8b%e8%bb%a2%e5%84%aa%e8%89%af%e4%ba%8b%e6%a5%ad%e6%89%80%e3%81%ab%e9%81%b8%e5%87%ba%e3%81%95%e3%82%8c%e3%81%be%e3%81%97%e3%81%9f%ef%bc%81%ef%bc%81/\">\n                        <div class=\"info_date\">2026/06/14</div>\n                        <div class=\"info_tag tag_infomation\">お知らせ</div>\n                        <p>安全運転優良事業所に選出されました！！</p>\n                    </a></li>\n                    \n                        \n                    \n                    <li><a href=\"https://jsg-system.com/info/2026/05/26/%e8%ad%a6%e5%82%99%e5%93%a1%e5%8b%9f%e9%9b%86%ef%bc%81%ef%bc%81/\">\n                        <div class=\"info_date\">2026/05/26</div>\n                        <div class=\"info_tag tag_infomation\">お知らせ</div>\n                        <p>警備員募集！！</p>\n                    </a></li>\n                    \n                        \n                    \n                    <li><a href=\"https://jsg-system.com/info/2026/04/23/%e8%87%aa%e8%bb%a2%e8%bb%8a%e3%81%ae%e9%9d%92%e5%88%87%e7%ac%a6/\">\n                        <div class=\"info_date\">2026/04/23</div>\n                        <div class=\"info_tag tag_infomation\">お知らせ</div>\n                        <p>自転車の青切符</p>\n                    </a></li>\n                    \n                        \n                    \n                    <li><a href=\"https://jsg-system.com/info/2026/04/09/%e6%98%a5%e3%81%ae%e5%85%a8%e5%9b%bd%e4%ba%a4%e9%80%9a%e5%ae%89%e5%85%a8%e9%81%8b%e5%8b%95%e3%82%b9%e3%82%bf%e3%83%bc%e3%83%88%ef%bc%81/\">\n                        <div class=\"info_date\">2026/04/09</div>\n                        <div class=\"info_tag tag_infomation\">お知らせ</div>\n                        <p>春の全国交通安全運動スタート！</p>\n                    </a></li>\n                    \n                                                              \n                </ul>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"info_more info_more_sp wow animated fadeInUp delay_next\">\n                <a href=\"/info/\" class=\"slidebtn\"><span class=\"slidebtn_font\">一覧を見る</span><span class=\"icon_arrow\"></span></a>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>    \n\n    \n<section class=\"wp-block-group top_service\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group inner\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<h2 class=\"top_h2 min wow animated fadeInUp\"><span>SERVICE</span>サービス紹介</h2>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"top_service_lead wow animated fadeInUp\">私たちは「安全・安心」な地域社会を形成する一端を担っています。</p>\n</div></div>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns service_list is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-9d6595d7 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column wow animated fadeInUp is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group service_list_ttl min\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n施設警備\n<span>INSTITUTION</span>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"service_list_lead\">金沢市内で官公庁、オフィスビル、外資系ホテル、列車警乗など幅広くサービスを提供しております。</p>\n\n\n\n<a href=\"/institution/\" class=\"slidebtn\"><span class=\"slidebtn_font\">詳細を見る</span><span class=\"icon_arrow\"></span></a>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column wow animated fadeInUp delay_fast is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group service_list_ttl min\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n機械警備\n<span>MACHINE</span>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"service_list_lead\">金沢市を中心に能登方面も対応しています。常時警備員が待機しており、即応体制を確保しております。</p>\n\n\n\n<a href=\"/machine/\" class=\"slidebtn\"><span class=\"slidebtn_font\">詳細を見る</span><span class=\"icon_arrow\"></span></a>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column wow animated fadeInUp delay_next is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group service_list_ttl min\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n交通誘導警備\n<span>TRAFFIC GUIDANCE</span>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"service_list_lead\">工事現場やイベント会場など車両と人が行きかう雑多な現場で「安全」を確保し、「安心」できる空間を提供しております。</p>\n\n\n\n<a href=\"/traffic_guidance/\" class=\"slidebtn\"><span class=\"slidebtn_font\">詳細を見る</span><span class=\"icon_arrow\"></span></a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div></section>\n\n\n\n<section class=\"wp-block-group top_company\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group inner clearfix\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group company_photo wow animated fadeInRight\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1000\" height=\"727\" src=\"https://jsg-system.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/company.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-223\" srcset=\"https://jsg-system.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/company.png 1000w, https://jsg-system.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/company-300x218.png 300w, https://jsg-system.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/company-768x558.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" /></figure>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group company_info wow animated fadeInLeft delay_next\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group company_info_inner\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading top_h2 min\"><span>COMPANY</span>企業情報</h2>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"top_company_lead\">私たちは「人」を介する施設警備を通じて、「安全・安心な地域社会」を形成するために邁進して参ります。</p>\n\n\n\n<a href=\"/company/\" class=\"slidebtn\"><span class=\"slidebtn_font\">詳細を見る</span><span class=\"icon_arrow\"></span></a>\n</div></div>\n</div></div>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group top_company_bg wow animated fadeInLeft\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\"></div></div>\n</div></section>\n\n<footer>\n    <div class=\"footer_contact\">\n        <div class=\"inner\">\n            <a href=\"/contact/\"><span>お問い合わせ</span></a>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"footer_info\">\n        <div class=\"inner\">\n            <div class=\"footer_info_box\">\n                <div class=\"footer_signiture\">\n                    <div class=\"footer_tit\"><img src=\"/wordpress/wp-content/themes/nkh/common/images/logo.svg\" alt=\"日本海警備保障\"></div>\n                    <div class=\"footer_address\">\n                        〒920-0376<br>\n                        石川県金沢市福増町北1377番地2<br>\n                        電話番号：076-255-7711<br>\n                        FAX番号：076-255-7195\n                    </div>\n\t\t\t\t<!--\n                    <div class=\"footer_sns\">\n                        <a href=\"\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://jsg-system.com/wordpress/wp-content/themes/nkh/common/images/sns_tw.svg\" alt=\"\"></a>\n                        <a href=\"\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://jsg-system.com/wordpress/wp-content/themes/nkh/common/images/sns_fb.svg\" alt=\"\"></a>\n                    </div>\n-->\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"footer_link\">\n                    <div class=\"footer_nav\">\n                        <nav>\n                            <ul>\n                                <li><a href=\"/\">HOME</a></li>\n                            </ul>\n                            <ul>\n                                <li><a href=\"/company/\">企業情報</a></li>\n                            </ul>\n                            <ul>\n                                <li><a href=\"javascript: void(0)\" class=\"nolink\">サービス紹介</a></li>\n                                <li class=